She chuckled, looking at Unitron. "He's got you running programs too 
I see." she smiled at him and rested her hands on her hips. Flicking 
her tail behind her and purring slightly.  She looked at HotRod who 
was still on the table. She then looked back at Unitron.Seeing his 
discontent and knowing how he was feeling. "I know what your 
thinking, you'd rather be out there slagging a few maximals in battle 
other than staying her working on the mundane. I know that feeling. 
This is so boring." She walked back to her console. "I still got a 
few hours left on mine, yours will take longer. Got any cards?" She 
smiled almost innocently at him.
